{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884326026,"sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","part":{"id":"prt_d7af3a245001ero0DtBB6VaEGx","messageID":"msg_d7af34d0c001dcnKSySm4mpt2c","sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/design.md","content":"# AR-020 Design: CLI pack 命令\n\n## Overview\n\nImplement the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI to package agent code,\nconfiguration, and dependencies into a distributable archive.\n\n## Command Interface\n\n### Usage\n\n```bash\nagentcube pack [OPTIONS] [PATH]\n```\n\n### Options\n\n- `--format, -f`: Archive format (tar.gz, zip). Default: tar.gz\n- `--output, -o`: Output file path. Default: auto-generated\n- `--verbose, -v`: Verbose output\n- `--dry-run`: Show what would be packed without creating archive\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n> TBD: Document key design decisions here.\n\n## Archive Structure\n\n```\nagent-name-v1.0.0.tar.gz\n├── agent.yaml          # Agent configuration\n├── src/                # Source code\n├── requirements.txt    # Python dependencies (if applicable)\n└── README.md          # Documentation\n```\n\n## References\n\n- [Python tarfile module](https://docs.python.org/3/library/tarfile.html)\n- [Python zipfile module](https://docs.python.org/3/library/zipfile.html)\n- [gitignore pattern matching](https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/design.md","time":{"start":1775884326002,"end":1775884326025}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884326028,"sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","part":{"id":"prt_d7af3c64d001g0mW8f4yBMQd1n","messageID":"msg_d7af34d0c001dcnKSySm4mpt2c","sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/notes.md","content":"# AR-020 Notes & References\n\n## Context\n\nThis change implements the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI, enabling\nusers to package their agent code into distributable archives.\n\n## Conventions\n\n- Python module naming: snake_case\n- CLI commands: kebab-case\n- Archive naming: {agent-name}-{version}.{format}\n- Configuration file: agent.yaml\n\n## Related Changes\n\n> Link to related ARs once they exist.\n\n## Open Questions\n\n> Document any open questions or decisions pending.\n\n## References\n\n- [Python argparse](https://docs.python.org/3/library/argparse.html)\n- [Click documentation](https://click.palletsprojects.com/)\n- [pathspec for gitignore](https://pypi.org/project/pathspec/)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/notes.md","time":{"start":1775884326004,"end":1775884326027}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884326030,"sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","part":{"id":"prt_d7af3df2c001b4PtK3ViS2HnD1","messageID":"msg_d7af34d0c001dcnKSySm4mpt2c","sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/tests.md","content":"# AR-020 Test Plan\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Command Line Interface\n\n- Test argument parsing\n- Test default values\n- Test invalid arguments handling\n\n### Archive Creation\n\n- Test .tar.gz creation\n- Test .zip creation\n- Test archive content verification\n\n### File Collection\n\n- Test gitignore pattern matching\n- Test file exclusion logic\n- Test edge cases (empty directories, symlinks)\n\n### Configuration Validation\n\n- Test valid configuration detection\n- Test invalid configuration error handling\n- Test missing required fields\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n- Test full pack workflow\n- Test with sample agent projects\n- Test large file handling\n\n## Test Commands\n\n```bash\n# Run all tests\npython -m pytest tests/cli/pack/\n\n# Run with coverage\npython -m pytest --cov=cmd.cli.pack tests/\n\n# Manual test\npython -m agentcube.cli pack ./my-agent --format tar.gz -o my-agent.tar.gz\n```\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/tests.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/tests.md","time":{"start":1775884326007,"end":1775884326029}}}}
