{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884326403,"sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","part":{"id":"prt_d7af3556a001r1vTa7DsIksyFg","messageID":"msg_d7af34d0c001dcnKSySm4mpt2c","sessionID":"ses_2850d43dcffeGq4jKQIv5xkeh0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-020\ntitle: CLI pack 命令\nmodule: cmd/cli\nlanguage: Python\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-020: CLI pack 命令\n# Module: cmd/cli\n# Language: Python\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: cli-command\n  description: |\n    Implement the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI. This command packages\n    agent code, configuration, and dependencies into a distributable format\n    (e.g., tarball or zip) that can be deployed to the AgentCube platform.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - cmd/cli/pack command implementation\n    - Pack command flags and options\n    - Archive creation logic\n    - Configuration validation\n    - Progress reporting\n  out:\n    - Upload functionality (separate command)\n    - Remote build process\n    - Docker image generation\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - Pack command creates valid archive files\n  - Supports .tar.gz and .zip formats\n  - Validates agent configuration before packing\n  - Excludes unnecessary files (respects .gitignore)\n  - Provides progress feedback during packing\n  - Returns proper exit codes\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://docs.python.org/3/library/tarfile.html\n  - https://docs.python.org/3/library/zipfile.html\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_202604